Trump, and he's going

24:42.948 --> 24:44.616 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to raise money for Republicans.

24:44.616 --> 24:47.086 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What do you make of this?

24:47.086 --> 24:49.588 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Well, first, the
RNC gathering, from what one can
tell, it's like the gathering

24:49.588 --> 24:50.656 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
