family in 1916.

24:50.656 --> 24:52.458 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

24:52.458 --> 24:56.362 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: They seem to have
no spine, no argument. All they
want is, they don't

24:56.362 --> 25:00.199 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
want the show in Cleveland to be
bad. And so as long as the show
is good, we can have

25:00.199 --> 25:03.402 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
