who will destroy the party.

25:03.402 --> 25:08.207 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so they're fine as long as
there is no bad drama. And so
they're laying down. And

25:08.207 --> 25:10.309 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Reince Priebus will go down as
one of the worst RNC heads for
what he -- how he's behaved

25:10.309 --> 25:12.444 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
this year.

25:12.444 --> 25:17.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Second, as for Donald Trump and
what Paul Manafort said, A, it's
not credible. Donald

25:17.950 --> 25:21.854 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Trump has been Donald Trump for
