25:21.854 --> 25:28.994 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that a voluble, large, loud,
and sometimes obnoxious and
sometimes appalling campaigner.

25:28.994 --> 25:32.664 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
He's not going to turn
presidential, because he lacks
the gravitas, he lacks the
knowledge

25:32.664 --> 25:37.770 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
