opportunist who's been putting

25:41.373 --> 25:44.176 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on a show all this time.

25:44.176 --> 25:46.278 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I don't -- I don't -- A,
don't think it's going to work,
and I don't think it's
particularly

25:46.278 --> 25:47.446 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
attractive either.

25:47.446 --> 25:49.114 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mark, what
do you think? Is it...

25:49.114 --> 25:51.750 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: I think it's
quite attractive. I really do.

25:51.750 --> 25:53.485 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

25:53.485 --> 25:57.923 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: Judy, I think the
Republican Party chair's
responsibility, any party chair,

25:57.923 --> 26:01.894 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
