from here forward.

27:12.631 --> 27:16.935 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, you
mentioned a changing position.
He was -- one of the things that

27:16.935 --> 27:20.906 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
