27:34.820 --> 27:35.921 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
this is not the
Republican position.

27:35.921 --> 27:37.623 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID BROOKS: Yes.

27:37.623 --> 27:39.258 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, that law is so bad, now I
have to praise Donald Trump.

27:39.258 --> 27:39.858 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

27:39.858 --> 27:42.661 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: And so he's right.

27:42.661 --> 27:46.398 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, he made the obvious
point. Is this really a problem
here? Like, are there a lot

27:46.398 --> 27:49.701 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of bathrooms at North Carolina
where people are scared to go
in? I don't think this is

27:49.701 --> 27:56.074 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
